article_title: Images Appear to Show Russian Artillery Targeting Ukrainian Town
article_text:
BRUSSELS—U.S. officials released photos Saturday they said showed Russian artillery targeting the strategic Ukrainian town of Debaltseve in the days and hours before a cease-fire was set to take effect.

“Russian military—not separatist, RU military—deployed [weapons] around Debaltseve where it is shelling [Ukrainian] positions,” tweeted Dan Baer, the U.S. ambassador to the Organization for Security and Cooperation in Europe, who was...
